What is Matplotlib ?
    ->Matplotlib is 3D and 2D plotting python library.
    ->It produce high quality graph.
    ->It also support animation.
It is written in python

Matplotlib graph
    ->Histrogram
    ->Bar Charts
    ->Scatterplots
    ->Area plot
    ->pie plot
    ->Error Charts
    ->Power Spectre

Dependancy
    It depend on NumPy

Installation of Matplotlib
    in terminal   pip install matplotlib

how to import?
    2 ways:-
        from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
                        or                  
        import matplotlib.pyplot as plt